        {
            "title": "珍惜生命│天水圍15歲男生墮樓 送院不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"15歲男生校內墮樓亡。劉權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c2f11ab69a5cba87ce4d53c8b8c1822e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031415310587129.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">15歲男生校內墮樓亡。劉權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>天水圍天瑞路一間中學，今（14日）早上11時51分，一名15歲男生，在校內由高處墮下，倒臥地面，昏迷不醒。救護員接報到場將他送院，惜最終搶救不治。警方正調查事件。該校辜副校長表示校園自殺案「一單都嫌多」，並指校方已通報教育局、啟動應變危機小組，以及有社工對師生進行輔導，稍後該校亦會發出新聞稿交代事件。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137185/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"學校發生男生墮樓事件。劉漢權攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7b48c7340e3c9512636c43177d69105/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_152015993_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        學校發生男生墮樓事件。劉漢權攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137186/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b13099da794c28bc6aa0ec84a4f9a469/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_152015993_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137187/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec2792fc9f9a22846929cb1984fb6b71/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250314_152015993_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
