            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "浙江狗狗走丟  自己到派出所「報案」｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/b0cdf8f2009e71f0955a87c7361c0102/036653c651754c48991a50f0bea9920b-492c6b36921f71a62254938bb9347de0-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d3d791d1113\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d3d791d1115\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7d86dced967504dbca83553ea2056031/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031415031747885.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日，浙江台州一隻邊牧牧羊犬走失，竟自己前往派出所「報案」，後成功與主人團聚。網友紛紛驚歎「太聰明了！」「狗是狗，邊牧是邊牧」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce41a4b5c6972b91e2c8b9ff0f2b1770/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_53_346ea84a_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/892ed354768583bcb389025982b92152/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_54_a258cb70_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/95d44bc8cc71d3d14ff8ead048b20f3e/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_53_f920ddb3_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7151887d93c46294821df71758c33c40/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_54_8981d17b_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cedfb9a1e8ce2f4c784cd9d7245f7d22/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_53_620c00e9_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/108708aa74d0f91052ea4e8c245d30ad/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_54_3ccddf8b_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浙江台州一隻走失的邊牧竟自己前往派出所「報案」。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"走失的邊牧與其主人團聚。抖音@椒江公安\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb17c5069c8d174d1ad1bfb3cc2cb265/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1414_13_53_ea7db084_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        走失的邊牧與其主人團聚。抖音@椒江公安\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3427642/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%96%AE%E8%BA%AB%E7%8B%97%E6%B5%81%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5-%E6%84%9B%E5%BF%83%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%B0%8B%E6%84%9B%E7%8A%AC\">深圳「單身狗」流落地鐵 愛心網友助主人尋愛犬</a>\n</p>\n<p>據椒江公安消息，近日，台州椒江前所派出所溜進一隻邊牧狗，賴在所裏不走，且身上沒有項圈和家養標識，只好暫時收編所裏，由民警輪流看護。後民警在抖音平台見到一條尋狗啟事，私信狗主人核對後，確認這隻邊牧正是其走失的狗狗。狗主人驚訝表示，「（狗狗）走失一個禮拜了，找了很多地方，沒想到自己來報案了。」\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3389900/%E5%BB%A3%E8%A5%BF%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%85%E5%8D%8A%E5%A4%9C%E8%B5%B7%E7%81%AB-%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%82%E5%8F%AB%E6%95%91%E5%85%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">廣西住宅半夜起火 醒目狗狂叫救全家︱有片</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
